분석1. 항공 출발 지연 데이터 분석¶

1.SQL 처리¶

In [6]:
depcount_by_month_by_year_sql =
sdf_sql(sc, "
            select year, month, count(*) as n 
            from ontime 
            where depdelay is not null
            and depdelay > 0
            group by year, month
            order by year, month
") %>% collect()

head(depcount_by_month_by_year_sql,5)

2.dplyr처리¶

In [7]:
depcount_by_month_by_year_dqplyr =
ontime_tbl %>% filter(!is.na(DepDelay)) %>% filter(DepDelay>0) %>% count(Year, Month) %>% arrange(Year,Month) %>% collect()

In [8]:
library(repr)
options(repr.plot.width=10,repr.plot.height=3) #비율

plot_df1 %>% ggplot(aes(month,n,color=year))+geom_line()+scale_x_discrete(limits=1:12, labels=paste(1:12, " M"))
